 @{b}SHOW_DT.dopus5@{ub}
 ================
Universelle Animationsanzeigescripte f³r Opus5. Formate:

- CDXL      (Amiga Multimediaformat Video + Audio)
- AVI       (Windows Multimediaformat Video + Audio) ausser Indeo-Kompression
